Environment Variables

Globally scoped variables:
pipeline {
agent any
environment {
MAX SIZE = 10
MIN SIZE = 1
}

Locally scoped variables:
pipeline {
stages {
stage ('Scale by 10×') {
environment {
MAX SIZE = 100
MIN SIZE = 10
}
}
}
}

Reference 2 ways
1- echo env.MAX_SIZE  #env keyword with lowercase with dot and name of variable 
2- echo MAX SIZE 

String env variable = dollar sign

echo "§env.MAX_SIZE"
echo "§{env.MAX_SIZE}"
echo "SMAX SIZE"
echo "S{MAX SIZE}"









